{"text_id":173983,"tokens":["In"," our"," work",","," we"," propose"," a"," novel"," approach"," to"," asset"," pricing",","," which"," we"," term"," information","-","based"," asset"," pricing","."," We"," depart"," from"," traditional"," methods"," that"," rely"," on"," firm"," characteristics"," or"," macroeconomic"," variables",","," and"," instead",","," focus"," on"," the"," information"," set"," of"," investors","."," Our"," key"," idea"," is"," that"," investors","'"," information"," processing"," and"," learning"," from"," available"," data"," drive"," asset"," prices","."," We"," develop"," a"," methodology"," that"," lever","ages"," machine"," learning"," algorithms"," and"," natural"," language"," processing"," techniques"," to"," quantify"," the"," information"," flow"," and"," its"," impact"," on"," asset"," prices","."," Specifically",","," we"," analyze"," large","-","scale"," textual"," data"," from"," various"," sources",","," including"," financial"," news",","," social"," media",","," and"," company"," reports",","," to"," capture"," the"," sentiment",","," tone",","," and"," content"," of"," investor"," communications","."," Our"," approach"," allows"," us"," to"," estimate"," the"," information","-","based"," risk"," premium",","," which"," reflects"," the"," compensation"," investors"," demand"," for"," bearing"," uncertainty"," related"," to"," information"," processing","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," information","-","based"," risk"," premium"," is"," a"," significant"," driver"," of"," asset"," returns",","," and"," its"," inclusion"," improves"," the"," predictive"," power"," of"," traditional"," asset"," pricing"," models","."," Furthermore",","," we"," find"," that"," our"," approach"," can"," capture"," time","-","varying"," risk"," premia"," and"," provides"," insights"," into"," the"," sources"," of"," market"," volatility","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}